high_descs: Turn right. When you reach the corridor, turn left. Reach the bathroom. Turn right. Turn left. Approach the bathtub.
Turn around. Continue forward to the bed, turn right, continue forward, turn left. Go forward to the window, turn right at the floorlamp. Go up the spraybottle.
anns.task_desc: Find the spraybottle and then turn on a floorlamp.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near bathtub
Pick up spray bottle from the bathtub
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the floor lamp on your right
anns.task_desc: Examine a spray bottle by the light of a floor lamp

high_descs: Walk towards and turn right to the bath tub.
Pick the spray bottle from the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Examine a spray bottle by the light of a tall lamp.
